data.description: Great opportunity to move into the top-rated Zachary School District with this beautiful 4BR home! The "Carencro” home offers a spacious kitchen and center island open to a bright 5-window breakfast/dining area. The kitchen features granite slab countertops, Stainless Appliances with a Gas Cooktop and tons of cabinets. Family Room includes wood floor and granite fireplace surround…Master suite features wood floor, trey ceiling, double vanities and huge master closet. A covered back porch is great for entertainment! Upgrades include crown molding faux wood blinds throughout. This is a must see!!!! No flood insurance required. This home is move-in-ready.
